videos.headline: Missouri's failed INT leads to go-ahead 2-point conversion for Arkansas
videos.description: Jamal Brooks nearly intercepts the ball, but bobbles it to allow Mike Woods to catch the 2-point conversion for Arkansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Missouri's failed INT leads to go-ahead 2-point conversion for Arkansas) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Missouri survives late-game 2-point conversion blunder
videos.description: After Arkansas tallied a go-ahead 2-point conversion off a bobble pass, Missouri comes back to kick a game-winning field goal as time expires.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Missouri survives late-game 2-point conversion blunder) 2020/12/05 ESHEET
